 * protocol, asset, APY, and TVL filters. Results are paginated and
 * sorted server-side.
 *
 * @param context - The EarnKit context containing providers
 * @param params - Vault discovery parameters
 * @returns A promise resolving to the matching vaults with pagination metadata
 * @throws {@link KitError} If validation fails, no provider is configured,
