/**
 * Poll a cross-chain Earn deposit until it reaches a terminal bridge state.
 *
 * Cross-chain deposits are long-running (source burn → CCTP attestation →
 * destination mint), so this is the primary way to observe completion. The
 * polling, terminal detection, and per-poll `status` step events live in the
 * provider (mirroring how the same-chain deposit phases emit events); this kit
 * operation validates input, selects the provider, and delegates.
 *
